values: Well I know i was just here but I didnt tell ya'll bout the Warped Tour...It WAS KICK ASS!!!! me and paige stayed up all night andleft my house at 8:30 and got there at 9:30...my dad gave us 60 bucks and bought us cameras...we sat outside the gates for about 45 mins but we met some hot and pretty tyte guys...they opened the main gate but kept the concert area shut for about another hour...me and paige sat on a hill and just chilled...I lost my pack of smokes before we even got in..they opened the doors and me and paige lost it...we went and bought T-Shirts...my is a MCR shirt...its a bitch gettin her throat slit by a shadow and on the back it says: shhhh...ur beautiful just the way u are. Paiges shirt is a Dropkick Murphy's shirt that says: KISS ME I'M SHITFACED!!! then we went and looked around...we found a good band playing and we started jumpin around and moshin kinda but then these 2 guys started actually fightin so we left there....we got to the TRUTH tent (the stop smokin commericial people) and we won free t-shirts there too...paige won for havin animal print underwear and i won for havin a tampon in my purse. after that we went and got somethin to drink....we got into another mosh pit and had sooo much fun....then we went over to the main stage to see my band play...i conned paige into going crowd surfing...she had a blast...then we walked around and got more free stuff...Trojan has a new condom out called mint tingle...its the after after dinner mint!!! HAHAHA!!! but yeah then we went in to a bass show and relaxed and got massages there!!! I stopped at the undead tent and got my face painted up!!! i looked like i had been murdered!! we went back to the main stage to see FALL OUT BOY...we smoke a doobie with total strangers then a girl fell on my head and i got a concussion!!! Woo Woo...after that we sat down on a hill and called my dad to tell him to come get us from the concert at 9 pm...well we ran outta money so i had to go the paramedics tent and tell them i needed ice for my head....me and paige ate it...we looked around some more and found the rap tent...these local boys were tearin it up and this bitch MC she was bad as hell...then i got overheated dehydrated and dizzy form my head...my dad came and got us at like 6 instead...we didnt go right home tho...my dad took me adn paige fishin for a couple hours...i didnt catch nothin but paige caught liek 10 fish...we went to her house and i seen Gavin for the first time...he is sooo perfect....then i came home and fought with my mom and then i passed the fuck out!!!
